This paper proposes a new type of variational autoencoder (VAE) that uses a Dirichlet prior for the continuous latent variable. The paper focuses on the performance of the model in classification tasks and topic modeling. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
